Hot Nurses (1976)

Starring: John Holmes, Crystal Sync, Eric Edwards, Marlene Willoughby, Zebedy Colt
Categories: Classic
Date Added: 1976
(958 Mb)

At Carcinoma Hospital patients are dying left and right under the unsepervised care of Doctor Matt, who is always distracted by the ample supply of "Hot Nurses" who work at the hospital. To improve profits, a radical new program is introduced with the pharmacy supplying liquor- not medicine, and the nurses will practice oral sex instead of alcohol rubs. Ambulances will become traveling motels and bed making will shift into orgies. As a result of this drastic policy change, the hospital becomes financially successful while the doctors, nurses and patients reap the rewards!
